WEBVTT

00:02:28.187 --> 00:02:31.980
what we are willing to give

00:02:32.004 --> 00:02:33.805
and what we give up.

00:02:35.655 --> 00:02:37.855
And also, what's important to us.

00:02:38.711 --> 00:02:43.001
Those conversations should be happening
in a good marriage,

00:02:43.025 --> 00:02:45.248
not after it is broken.

00:02:46.549 --> 00:02:51.065
Because when you wait until it's broken,

00:02:51.089 --> 00:02:52.239
it's too late.

00:02:52.914 --> 00:02:55.009
But if you have them early on,

00:02:55.033 --> 00:02:58.165
they can actually help build
a better marriage.

00:02:59.228 --> 00:03:01.633
Three ideas that I want
to put on the table